Steps to clone and Use

$> git clone http://github.com/shreekavi/erlang-app-structure.git

Rename the folder erlang-app-structure to a folder name of your choice

Remove references to the this repo and create references to your own repo.

$> git remote rm origin

Check the configuration using

$> git config -l

Add a remote branch to this repo.

$> git remote add origin git@github.com/account/your-repo.git


